FBIS3-42256 "jptot006__l94068" JPRS-TOT-94-006-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 9 February 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Seventeen Leftist `Terrorists' Captured in Malatya TA0302154794 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1425 GMT 3 Feb 94 TA0302154794 Ankara ANATOLIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Malatya, Feb 3 (AA) -- Seventeen terrorists belonging to an outlawed leftist terrorist organization were captured following security operations in southeastern Malatya Province, it was reported on Thursday. A written statement from Malatya Mayor's Office said the terrorists were captured following joint operations by security headquarters and the gendarmerie forces to the terrorists safe-houses in the city. Firearms, ammunitions and money were seized following the searches of the safe-house, it added.
